data.description: Welcome to this delightful 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom gem nestled in the heart of Norristown. This end-of-row house offers a cozy and inviting atmosphere, with a host of modern amenities for your comfort and convenience. Seller is selling as is and buyer is responsible for the U & O Inspection.   Key Features:  LVP Flooring & Ceramic Tile: Enjoy the seamless flow and easy maintenance of Luxury Vinyl Plank flooring throughout the main level, while the kitchen boasts elegant ceramic tile, adding a touch of sophistication to the space.  Brand New Stainless Steel Appliances: The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring brand new, top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances that combine style and functionality seamlessly. Also, has white cabinets with granite countertops.   Small but Picturesque Backyard: Step outside to your own private oasis - a compact yet charming backyard space, perfect for relaxing, gardening, or hosting intimate gatherings.  New Hot Water Heater: Say goodbye to worries about chilly showers or unexpected maintenance issues with the recently installed hot water heater, ensuring your home runs smoothly.  $10k Seller's Assist: The generous seller is offering a $10,000 assistance, providing you with added flexibility and options as you make this house your own.   Convenience is key with this Norristown property. Situated in a highly accessible location, you'll find public transportation options, shopping, and a range of amenities just moments away. Whether you're commuting to work or exploring the local scene, you'll appreciate the ease of getting around. Don't miss out on the opportunity to call this charming end-of-row house your home. Schedule a viewing today and discover the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience that awaits you!
